    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th-percentile NIH below clinical threshold across the operating conditions described in the COU. The ContextOfUse description enumerates temperature, pressure, flow regime, and rotational speed ranges in sufficient narrative detail that reviewers may reasonably infer a bounded envelope; however, no formal hasOperatingEnvelope or hasApplicabilityConstraint link is asserted, leaving the model's valid range of use ontologically unspecified. Package accepted on the strength of factor evidence.",
